The U.S. Dollar convertible eurobond forKeppel Corp has been increased to 75 mln dlrs from the initial60 mln, bookrunner Morgan Grenfell and Co Ltd said.    The coupon was set at four pct compared with an indicationof four to 4-1/4 pct. The conversion price was set at 3.12Singapore dlrs per share, a premium of 5.05 pct. The foreignexchange rate was set at 2.1381 Singapore dlrs to the U.S.Dollar. REUTER&#3;